I am a web developer currently living in Austin, TX. I have two beautiful daughters and a wonderful wife.

Professionally, I enjoy solving complicated problems and building solutions that "just work". Nothing makes me happier than a few lines of elegant code.

In my free time I enjoy tasting beers, watching football, and riding my longboard.
